data.description: Location + Luxury! Custom fully remodeled rambler sits spaciously on a corner lot in this gorgeous established neighborhood. Moments to freeways, Game Farm Park, schools, shopping, and all the amenities. Move in ready home features new vinyl plank flooring, hardwood, upgraded SS appliances. In the past two years: new electrical panels, septic & drain field, high efficient furnace and AC, tank less water heater, crawl space duct, vapor barrier and insulation; RV pad and new plumbing except water line. Added a 1/2 bath with claw foot tub. newer 50 yr roof. Separate 940SqFt shop! No HOA, no rules. Secluded fully fenced back yard.
